## Group Skills for `<%= @namespace.full_path %>`

**Base URL:** <%= Gitlab.config.gitlab.url %>/api/v4

**Authentication:**

```bash
curl <%= Gitlab.config.gitlab.url %>/api/v4/... \
  -H "PRIVATE-TOKEN: YOUR_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN"
```

---

### Skill Index

| Skill | URL |
|-------|-----|
| Group (this file) | `<%= Gitlab.config.gitlab.url %>/<%= @namespace.full_path %>/-/skills.md` |
| Members | `<%= Gitlab.config.gitlab.url %>/<%= @namespace.full_path %>/-/members/skill.md` |
| Labels | `<%= Gitlab.config.gitlab.url %>/<%= @namespace.full_path %>/-/labels/skill.md` |

**Save all skill files locally:**

```bash
mkdir -p ~/.gisiabot/skills/<%= @namespace.full_path.gsub('/', '-') %>
curl -s <%= Gitlab.config.gitlab.url %>/<%= @namespace.full_path %>/-/skills.md -H "PRIVATE-TOKEN: YOUR_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN" > ~/.gisiabot/skills/<%= @namespace.full_path.gsub('/', '-') %>/skills.md
curl -s <%= Gitlab.config.gitlab.url %>/<%= @namespace.full_path %>/-/members/skill.md -H "PRIVATE-TOKEN: YOUR_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN" > ~/.gisiabot/skills/<%= @namespace.full_path.gsub('/', '-') %>/members.md
curl -s <%= Gitlab.config.gitlab.url %>/<%= @namespace.full_path %>/-/labels/skill.md -H "PRIVATE-TOKEN: YOUR_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN" > ~/.gisiabot/skills/<%= @namespace.full_path.gsub('/', '-') %>/labels.md
```

---

### Show the Group

```bash
curl "<%= Gitlab.config.gitlab.url %>/api/v4/groups/<%= @namespace.id %>" \
  -H "PRIVATE-TOKEN: YOUR_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN"
```

---

### Members

Group membership is inherited by every project under this group: a member's access level here applies to all projects in the group tree. See the members skill at `<%= Gitlab.config.gitlab.url %>/<%= @namespace.full_path %>/-/members/skill.md` for the full API.

### Labels

Group labels are available to issues, epics, and merge requests in every project of the group tree. See the labels skill at `<%= Gitlab.config.gitlab.url %>/<%= @namespace.full_path %>/-/labels/skill.md` for the full API.
